{"tid":1268270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係文宣素材收集日","createTime":"2019-06-30T08:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:06:17.000Z","uid":199829,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f50a3526a8aff0b9ca69b3333ccb22cc1611e5","tid":1268270,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"記住啦，牆被毀壇被拆唔緊要，聽日再起過！<br />\n<br />\n物資盡量保護，保護唔到被毀都唔緊要，再捐過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要係。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攞手機影得哂所有拆野過程，千奇唔好同d廢老廢中嘈，更加唔係同佢有身體接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢老廢中最多都係出黎今日，我地來日方長，有咁多咁好既素材做文宣，唔係唔收集呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"9971a3d0346fdfe292e2fb4d6aa324cd3f1c9119","tid":1268270,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c697a65cbf634b97081b114d302dc083dc820e9","tid":1268270,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"404c4dd8c0b7ba2c0600181b0dd8193f6542146e","tid":1268270,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"507ad63caf85859cc0393219d58363904cf19e95","tid":1268270,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6aa25a4bed838c9b669a47a9e48995b1ece458df","tid":1268270,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"edf7f1c2415130410185d8231064e2079ba64592